    <h1 class="mb-4">Best AI Search Strategy for Small Business 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on testing across UK small businesses</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Small businesses have an advantage in AI search that most do not realise. AI platforms reward clarity over size. A focused local business with a well-structured website can appear on ChatGPT and Gemini ahead of national brands with larger budgets.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">The strategies below are ranked specifically for small businesses: limited budget, limited time, no in-house marketing team.</p>

